Bugs:
    ✔ when shutting down with the UI button, the socket cannot reconnect @done(26-01-18 12:35)
    ☐ when loading a firmware and closing the emulator, the string on the config file of windows does not escape backlashes properly
    ☐ In init window, we have to hack the hidpi, seems it broke a little bit ago in raylib?
    ☐ Wireframe 3d rendering works but draws some garbage
    ☐ Not a bug per se, but if ATE1 (echo) is enabled on the modem, and the CPU dares to echo back what it gets on the serial line, when answering a call and then escaping to command mode, a feedback loop will be triggered and possibly crash the emulator. This to say that if ATE1 is enabled you DONT NEVER EVER echo again.
    ✔ How does the video subsytem do DMA? all pointers passed to it are physical @done(26-01-29 21:39)
